*Malim* prstom je dotaknuo list papira. (He touched the paper with his little finger.)

Nisam *mala* žena pa da se plašim. (I'm not a small woman to be scared.)

Svi *mali* deca čekaju Božić. (All the little children are waiting for Christmas.)

*Malom* deci je potrebna pomoć. (Little children need help.)

Ona je nosila *malo* dete u naručju. (She was carrying a small child in her arms.)